(12, '穿越直布罗陀海峡，漫步伊比利亚半岛', '<div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-1" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">行程安排</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="mdd-zj" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172715_96530.jpg" width="600" height="400" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172715_22404.jpg" width="600" height="340" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172716_98586.jpg" width="600" height="375" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172717_45966.jpg" width="600" height="400" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172718_10050.jpg" width="600" height="400" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172719_27723.jpg" width="600" height="600" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172720_72831.jpg" width="600" height="450" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172722_74146.jpg" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20160203/20160203172722_53431.jpg" width="600" height="400" alt="" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 672px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">D1 里斯本-罗卡角-辛特拉- 夜宿巴达霍斯ca.250km</span></p><span style="font-size: 16px;">D2 巴达霍斯-梅里达-塞维利亚 ca.240km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D3 塞维利亚-哥多华（科尔多瓦）-格拉纳达 ca.140km+ca.227km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D4 格拉纳达-马拉加-米哈斯-Marbella ca.136km+ca.58km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D5-6 Marbella 4 Day IVV walking, 20 or 30km 每天，注册费40欧元 10月13-16日</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D7 Marbella-直布罗陀-阿尔希拉斯-轮渡丹吉尔&nbsp;</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">歐洲大陸的最南端—阿爾西拉斯</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D8 丹吉尔-梅克内斯-费斯 ca.281km+60km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D9 费斯-拉巴特 ca.208km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D10.拉巴特-卡萨布兰卡 ca.100km</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">D11.卡萨布兰卡-北京</span><br/></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-2" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">费用说明</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13.3333px;"><span style="color: rgb(229, 51, 51); font-size: 14px;">备注：</span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13.3333px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">（1）活动报名截止后，如活动参与人数不足最低人数，我们在取消活动安排后将活动预订款100元/人全额退回个人；</span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13.3333px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">（2）活动报名截止后，活动参与人员每人交纳活动确认款2900元/人；</span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 13.3333px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: normal;">（3）出签后，活动参与人员交齐余款。</span></p><span style="font-size: 13.3333px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">————————————————————</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.6666px;">————————————————————</span><span style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 16.6666px;">————————————————————</span></span></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-3" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">线路描述</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">最知性的深度旅程：</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★葡萄牙前往洛卡岬领取「欧洲最西点的证明书」，为人生留下最珍贵的永恒回忆。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★全览西班牙最有异国情调的安达鲁西亚三名城—塞维亚、格拉纳达、哥多华。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★阿维拉—由9个城门与88座浑实城垛围绕中古古城，并被联合国教科文组织收列为观光客绝对收藏之世界人类遗产。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★拜访诗人拜伦眼中的地上伊甸园—仙达皇宫，集合了阿拉伯摩尔式、哥德式、葡萄牙式的建筑风格及庭园造景，任何人皆不可错过的欧洲宫殿。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★MEZQUITA回教清真寺，此为伊斯兰及文艺复兴时期混合式的奇特建筑，内部由850根玛瑙碧玉般的大理石圆柱装饰而成，走入其中让人有进入迷宫的感觉，目前更是世界上唯一蔚为奇观的清真寺天主教教堂。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★「人间乐园」之阿尔罕布拉宫城堡区及宫殿区、查理五世宫殿、「天堂花园」之格内那利菲皇庭花园，宫内精巧的设计，缀以华丽的雕饰，庭园之内的喷泉水池、修剪整齐的花草，体现大食帝国的繁华宫殿及庭园建筑的特殊风格，堪称为精华代表作。</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★摩洛哥第二大城及第一个回教王朝之国都—费斯，费斯为摩洛哥一千多年来宗教、文化、艺术中心，也是四大皇城中历史最悠久古城</span><br/><span style="font-size: 16px;">★摩洛哥首都─拉巴特。此城于1912年，因对外联络往来便利之优势，由当时殖民国－法国，选为总督府所在。</span></div></div></div><p><br/></p>', '6', 11, '2017-09-09', '2017-09-20', 29000, '国外,', '格拉纳达（Granada）西班牙最末期的回教王朝，体验浓浓的摩尔风情。感受截然不同的西班牙南部风情。 卡萨布兰卡（Ca', '活动内容你说了算', '2017-09-09 8:00:00', '首都国际机场', '1', '230km', '自驾', 20, 0, '18328402805', '吉姆领队', '1504445120.jpg#1504445128.jpg#1504445139.jpg', '没有特色', '2017-09-04 03:26:28'),
(13, '大唔大的', '<p>123456</p>', '5', 5, '2017-10-15', '2017-10-15', 80, '红井路十渡', '青城山景点', '休闲穿越徒摄影聚会体育健身', '2017-09-01', '惠新西街', '23', '200km', '包车', 34, 0, '18328402805', '张翠翠领队', '1504533974.jpg#1504533976.jpg#1504533982.jpg', '特色', '2017-09-04 14:21:05'),
(14, '9.23-9.24闫家坪登顶海坨山 赏海坨秋色两日活动', '<p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">【活动行程】</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">9.23</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">周六晚</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">17</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">：</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">30</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">惠新西南口</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">C</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">出口；（就一站～公主坟不停车）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">19</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">：</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">30</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">龙庆峽村王家大院住宿农家院</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">9.24</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">早</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">5:00</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">起床</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">5:30</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">早餐</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">6:00</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">出发</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">7:00</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">抵达闫家坪，合影热身后，开始爬山</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">11:30</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">登顶小海坨山，天好多呆会。鞍部吃自带午餐。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">15:00</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">抵达大海坨村停车场。</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">预计</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">18:30</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">到达惠新西街南口结束愉快的行程！</span></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">费用说明</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">【费用名细】</span><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-family: NSimSun;font-size: 12px"><span style="color: rgb(229, 51, 51)">【活动费用】：</span><span style="color: rgb(229, 51, 51)">:20-30人190元，30人以上180元，无门票,含早餐和龙庆峽村农家院住宿</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">【费用包含】：往返大巴车费、保险、资料、</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">2</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">瓶水，领队，司机食宿。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"><br/></span></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">线路描述</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">【行走路线】</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">:&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">闫家坪～西大垭口～小海坨主峰～大海坨主峰</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">(</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">强驴可上</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">)</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">～马鞍部～大海坨村</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">【适合人群】：喜欢延庆海坨山，喜欢摄影，走过玉渡山大环线，后河，白草洼</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">28</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">公里的人群。时间充裕，可以在路上和山顶尽情拍照！</span><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">【路程难度】：</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">CVA 1.2,</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">徒步</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">&nbsp;14.5KM</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">，累计爬升</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">1070</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">米</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">,</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">下降</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">1100</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">米。是登顶海坨山</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">(</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">除了从大海坨村上</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">)</span><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: NSimSun">最近最缓最美的一条线路。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 宋体"><span style="font-family: NSimSun">【线路描述】：</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">闫家坪路线起点位于河北与北京交界处，海拔约</span><span style="font-size: 12px">1300</span><span style="font-size: 12px">多米，出发地点比西大庄科路线大约高</span><span style="font-size: 12px">400</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米，爬升海拔高度大约</span><span style="font-size: 12px">800</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米（小海坨顶峰</span><span style="font-size: 12px">2198.38</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米），总爬升高度大约</span><span style="font-size: 12px">1100</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米。路线长度大约有</span><span style="font-size: 12px">15</span><span style="font-size: 12px">公里，一路行走在山脊上，可俯瞰延庆周边平原和官厅水库，视线开阔，景色壮丽。路线上需要翻越</span><span style="font-size: 12px">7</span><span style="font-size: 12px">、</span><span style="font-size: 12px">8</span><span style="font-size: 12px">个小山丘，每个小丘高度从几十米到一百多米不等，因此还是有一定强度的。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">海坨山简介</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">海坨山位于延庆县张山营镇北部与河北省赤城县交界处，东南距延庆镇约</span><span style="font-size: 12px">18</span><span style="font-size: 12px">公里，属军都山。主峰小海坨海拔</span><span style="font-size: 12px">2241</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米，为北京市第二高峰。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">海坨山高峰有三个：大海坨、二海坨、三海坨。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">大海坨山顶是一个长</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">近</span><span style="font-size: 12px">10</span><span style="font-size: 12px">公里，宽</span><span style="font-size: 12px">500</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米，最窄处不过百米的草甸平缓山顶，南侧断裂升降显著，山势险峻。每年</span><span style="font-size: 12px">l0</span><span style="font-size: 12px">月至次年</span><span style="font-size: 12px">6</span><span style="font-size: 12px">月可以看到“海坨戴雪”。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 12px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="font-size: 12px">海坨山地形分布描述：海坨山分为大、小海坨，从延庆城向西北看去，能看见颜色与周围不同的三座“山”，中间为小海坨、右手面为大海坨，左手面为无名山。在三座山峰之间各还有</span><span style="font-size: 12px">2</span><span style="font-size: 12px">座小山丘，海拔都在</span><span style="font-size: 12px">2000</span><span style="font-size: 12px">米以上。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: 宋体"><span style="font-size: 14px;font-family: NSimSun"></span><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132245_24519.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132245_49557.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132246_36492.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132247_51760.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132404_44851.jpg" alt="" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132405_39486.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132405_18879.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="450" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170906/20170906132405_10591.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="600" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '8', 1, '2017-09-23', '2017-09-24', 180, '北京 延庆县', '延庆海坨山', '休闲 登山 徒步 摄影', '2017-09-23 12:12:12', '惠新西街南口C出口', '1.2', '200KM', '汽车', 34, 0, '18328402805', '西西领队', '1504875496.jpg#1504875501.jpg#1504875505.jpg#1504875509.jpg', '闫家坪登顶海坨山 赏海坨秋色两日活动 20-30人190元 30人以上180元 无门票 含早餐和龙庆峽村农家院住宿', '2017-09-08 13:14:45');
INSERT INTO `tubuhuodong` (`id`, `title`, `tuwen`, `types`, `howlong`, `startday`, `endday`, `price`, `mudidi`, `jingdian`, `neirong`, `jihetime`, `jihedidian`, `qiangdu`, `juli`, `jiaotong`, `need`, `baoming`, `phone`, `leader`, `pictures`, `tese`, `ptime`) VALUES
(15, '【精品】2017年十一高端人士徒步西藏墨脱（达级线路骨灰色）', '<hr/><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-1" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="mdd-zj" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 9px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">活动路线】：</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">西藏</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">林芝——派镇——拉格——汗密—背崩—墨脱——波密</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">——林芝</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 19px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">这是目前进出墨脱县最为常见和安全系数最高的徒步线路，也是一条可以让</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">您</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">游刃有余。</span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 19px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">1</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">9</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月29</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日） ——</span><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">林芝机场集合 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------宿派镇兄弟客栈</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">没时间</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">适应高反</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">，下午去雅鲁藏布大峡谷，晚上检查装备，去除多余的，剩下的寄回林芝宾馆，8天以后能见到行李。</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D2</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">9</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月30</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日）派镇----- 松林口——多雄拉山口&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;---</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">-- 宿拉格</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">客栈</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 21px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一路向上，行程36公里（坐卡车18公里）。第一天</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">如果</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">节省体力，乘坐派镇部队转运站或地方上的汽车前往松林口。（派镇往多雄拉山的方向有一条简易的林间公路</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">18公里左右</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">，一直通到松林口的地方，这段林间公路两旁的风景很美），从松林口开始正式徒步翻阅多雄拉至拉格</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">18公里</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">。（可以徒步上山） &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【徒步距离】</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">18公里 大约需要6—7小时</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【主要风景】</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">欣赏巍峨壮观的多雄拉雪山</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【最难】</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">必须在中午13点前翻过多雄拉雪山垭口</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 16px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">海拔逐渐升高，但是由于在中午1点钟之后山顶会浓雾弥漫、风雪交加，很容易让人迷失方向而发生危险，所有需要在中午1点钟以前翻过海拔4</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">3</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">00多米的山口。不过大家也不要太大压力，只要我们调整步伐，掌握一些翻阅雪山的技巧，过了垭口大家就可以慢慢欣赏雪山之美了！有些在多雄拉上遇难的归根结底主要是因为他们在“错误的时间来到了一个错误的地点”，他们是在不适合进出的季节也就是封山季节里试图侥幸通过而导致了严重的后果。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">【技巧】：上山用脚尖，下山用脚跟</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D3</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">10</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月1日）拉格——汗密</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">宿汗密客栈</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【距离】28公里</span><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">约8小时 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【主要景点】原始森林、大岩洞、小岩洞</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【最难】</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">1、</span><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">距离较长，原始森林的风景恐有看烦觉得累</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">2、</span><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">第一次“见识”蚂蟥的威力！在过了大岩洞之后不久就会进入蚂蝗区，大约行程还剩1-2小时</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">。</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 14px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">3、因为距离较长，烂泥路，泥里有坚硬石头，极其硌脚，穿军胶鞋在这里会觉得底薄。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D4</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">10</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月2</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日）汗密-老虎嘴-阿尼桥（一号桥）-二号桥-解放大桥</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp; ----</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">-</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">宿</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">背崩</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 16px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">这段路坡度很大，上午一路伴随着蚂蝗，路面俱为大大小小的石头，所以这段“老虎嘴”对于来往驮载重物的牲畜是道难关。道路的泥泞湿滑，使下山往墨脱方向去的它们往往在山道上跌跌撞撞的，每年雨季都会有大批牲畜因天雨路滑而摔下几百米深的山谷里去。因此，你在这一段路需要小心提防经过身边的牲畜，最好能及时给这些气喘吁吁控制不了自己身体的可怜家伙们让出路来，和它们错身时最好能靠到路内侧的岩壁边。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 21px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">过了二号桥之后有一个岔路口，还有另一条路，即走德兴到墨脱，距离近一些，但极不好走，建议走背崩。过解放大桥后就是一个边境检查站，再往前有驻扎部队。这里是军事重地，严禁拍摄，过桥时就要把摄影器材收起来，以免受到盘问甚至强行曝光。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【徒步距离】：32公里 约9——9小时 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D5</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">10</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月3</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日）背崩--亚让--墨脱</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;------</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">宿墨脱县城</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">伴随着雅鲁藏布江一路走，到达墨脱。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">比前几天路途平缓些，但是慢上坡考验你的意志...</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">已修好公路，坚持不了的坐车</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">—— 我们终于到达了墨脱！！</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 32px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">【徒步距离】：徒步3</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">2</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">公里 约8小时&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">（走不了可以有车了）</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><br/></span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 32px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D6</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">10</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月4</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日）墨脱-113K-108K-80K</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">-波密 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------宿波密</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 42px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">上午调整！/10点乘车（全程</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">越野</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">包车）</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">一路惊险不断，只选最好的当地司机才有把握把我们安全运送出去。景色美的地方还会徒步一段。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 35px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"><br/></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 35px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D7</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">/（</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">10</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">月5</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">日</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">）</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;波密——鲁朗----</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">林芝八一</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-------宿林芝</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 35px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;—— 如果一切正常... 这一天赏美景不用说......</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这一天会让你真正的懂得了“幸福感”是从来没有过的！......</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 39px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">如果麦通大桥已修好，半路有最天然的温泉，彻底缓解几天来的疲惫。</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">包车，早</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">7点</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">出发，边走边玩边泡......</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 39px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">下午</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">4:00前 抵达八一镇（林芝），</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">&nbsp;在八一最后的</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">晚</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">餐！&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">饭后活动结束，晚上自由活动狂欢</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;"></span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">第二天可以各奔东西。……</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">——彼此无语，含泪分别……</span><span class="15" style="font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">只有等待那时的回忆！……</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">D8/(10月6日）送站林芝机场，林芝没有火车站，只有上午的飞机。（有去拉萨的自己走吧）</span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">如果报名人数够10人，送其它景点。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-2" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">费用说明</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 9px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">8900</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">元/人；（非会</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">员9100</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">元）</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">费用包括：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">林芝机场----墨脱---林芝结束期间的，包含正餐、住宿、分段</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">越野</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">包车、向导马托夫等（不负重，轻装徒步）、保险和景区门票等全含。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 24px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">（抵离</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">林芝</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">前后的交通费用自理）</span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">【服务】 全程配备CVA专业户外领队，紧急救援</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">配备向导</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">，保证您的安全，赠送户外20万保险，必要时刻有空中救援服务。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">进墨脱前和出墨脱住地方3-4星宾馆，根据当地的条件，选择最好的车型，让您体会到有苦有乐的VIP待遇，吃饭标准选择当地特色。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">其他自理</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">费用</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：个人购物</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; text-align: justify; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">边防证办理</span><span style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">费用</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">墨脱南部为</span><a href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;"><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;">中国</span></a><a href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); outline: none; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;"><span class="15" style="font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 18px;">印度</span></a><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">边境争议地区，进入墨脱需要边防证。（请在当地或户籍处办理好边防证）</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">边防证在户口所在地办理起来比较方便，完全免费。在林芝没有时间办理，</span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">户口所在地办理流程：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">1</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">、到区公安局出入境管理窗口拿一张申请表格。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">2</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">、按照表格提示，先拿着身份证去单位人事部或社区居委会或村委会核实本人身份，盖章。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">、去街道派出所核实身份，查犯罪记录，盖章。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">、回到区公安局出入境管理窗口，当场拿到边防证。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">注意：有些地区在办理边防证时需要在里面贴照片，有些和身份证一起使用就不用照片，在第一步领取表格时向工作人员咨询。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-3" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">线路描述</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 24px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 16px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp;墨脱不但是户外驴友的天堂，也是近年来各大企业领军人物、拼搏在职场高级白领以及演艺界名流等有识之士的必选路线，他们把行走墨脱当成是自己的最终梦想，也把徒步墨脱作为能否在事业上更上一层楼的一场人生历练。登珠峰可以让您站得高看得远，走过墨脱可以让您大风大浪都不怕，会让您的事业更加有成，把控人生的能力更加精彩！来吧，您绝对不会后悔，中国徒步将提供给您最安全的保障，助您实现梦想！</span><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一、【活动时间】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp;2017</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">年&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">9&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">月</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;29&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">日</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;林芝机场集合----10月6日林芝解散</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">二、【活动</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">名称</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">高端人士徒步西藏墨脱</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">三、【活动</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">地点</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><span style="line-height: 24px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">西藏</span><span style="line-height: 24px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">林芝机场——派镇——拉格——汗密—背崩—墨脱——波密</span><span style="line-height: 24px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;;">——林芝</span></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">四、【</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">适合</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">人群】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">运动型、经常户外 &nbsp;CVA：2.0级</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">五、【</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">路程全长</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">连续徒步四天共115公里，上升1300米 ，最高海拔4300米</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">六、【集合地点】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">西藏---林芝机场</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">七、【活动领队】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">张姐 &nbsp;13381033689</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-size: 24px;">参加活动的朋友请加</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: rgb(146, 208, 80);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 80);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-size: 24px;">QQ群 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;徒步网一群：94419616</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;微博 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@中国徒步网</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;微信 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;微信号：chinawalking</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 176, 240); font-size: 24px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;二维码：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img title="公众号.jpg" src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/php/upload/97241448443146.jpg" width="200" height="194" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none; width: 200px; height: 194px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; font-size: 24px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/forum_travel</span><span style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);">view.php?newsid=61</span></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 20px;">张姐户外简历（第五次进墨脱）</span></p><div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">墨脱又名白马岗，是西藏最具神秘性的地方之一。西藏著名的宗教经典称：“佛之净土白马岗，圣地之中最殊胜。”这些受到信徒顶礼膜拜的圣地，给众多西藏人的心灵播下无限的诱惑，墨脱的门巴人、珞巴人说他们居住的地方叫“白隅欠布白马岗”，意思是“隐藏着的像莲花那样的圣地”。在佛教的观念里，莲花是吉祥的象征。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span class="15" style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">从派乡翻多雄拉雪山，经汗密、拉格、背崩，3～4天就可以到墨脱。目前，这条路是去墨脱的主要通道。回来是从雅鲁藏布上行到108公里处，再翻越嘎隆拉雪山到波密，需时3～4天。 具体行程： &nbsp; &nbsp; 米林——派乡：90公里行程。 &nbsp; &nbsp; 转运站——拉格：转运站距派乡5公里，是一个小集贸市场，有食宿。到松林口3小时, 汽车盘山道1.5小时到多雄拉山口，5小时到拉格，可以住宿。 &nbsp; &nbsp; 拉格——汗密：2.5小时到大岩洞，5小时到汗密，那里有一个兵站，几个接待站，可住宿。 &nbsp; &nbsp; 汗密——背崩乡：到阿尼桥4小时，再行7小时到背崩，住背崩乡。(注意：没办边防证要在八一镇武警边防大队办理边境证，因为过解放大桥检查站时要接受盘查。还有，不要拍摄大桥，过桥前把相机收好，以免被强行曝光)。 &nbsp; &nbsp; 背崩乡——墨脱：从背崩乡以北10小时到墨脱，这段小道较平缓，墨脱县城建在一个小山丘上。 &nbsp; &nbsp; 墨脱——波密：墨脱至波密108公里，开车4小时的行程，路途艰险，时有塌方。从坡密回林芝，麦通大桥施工，时常堵车。</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 32px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/upload/20151125/14484461013831.jpg" title="合影.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/upload/20151125/14484461034366.jpg" title="雪山.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/upload/20151125/1448446103801.jpg" title="3.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/upload/20151125/14484461053020.jpg" title="4.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><img src="http://new.chinawalking.net.cn/upload/20151125/1448446107677.jpg" title="5.jpg" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: initial; border-style: none;"/></p></div></div></div></div><p><br/></p>', '8', 7, '2017-09-30', '2017-10-6', 8900, '西藏,拉萨', '墨脱', '登山,穿越,徒步', '2017-09-01 12:12:12', '林芝', '2.0', '115km', '火车', 15, 0, '18328402805', '西西领队', '1504876857.jpg#1504876863.jpg#1504876867.jpg#1504876878.jpg#1504876883.jpg', '西藏墨脱徒步，2017年十一长假走墨脱', '2017-09-08 13:21:29');
INSERT INTO `tubuhuodong` (`id`, `title`, `tuwen`, `types`, `howlong`, `startday`, `endday`, `price`, `mudidi`, `jingdian`, `neirong`, `jihetime`, `jihedidian`, `qiangdu`, `juli`, `jiaotong`, `need`, `baoming`, `phone`, `leader`, `pictures`, `tese`, `ptime`) VALUES
(16, '2017年10月15日【红叶节】走红井路+游房山十渡，看遍山红叶', '<h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">行程安排</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">07:00&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">&nbsp; &nbsp;<strong style="font-family: Tahoma, Verdana"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">惠新西街南口C出口</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">&nbsp;07:30 &nbsp;<span style="line-height: 36px">公主坟新兴宾馆</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 64px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 8px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">09:00</span></strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">门头沟红井路入口</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 8px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 16px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 24px">13</span><strong><span style="font-size: 24px">:00 &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">山上吃自备午饭。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 8px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">15:30&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">下到房山十渡景区，有京津冀年票的可以进去。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 8px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">16:30&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">最晚上车返京时间</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 8px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">18:30</span></strong><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 24px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">到达北京出发地</span></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">费用说明</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">费用总计：会员80元 &nbsp; 非会员90元</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">包括：车费、保险、水、资料、领队。午餐自带，京津冀年卡有用</span></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">线路描述</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">一、【活动时间】： &nbsp;2017年 10月15日</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">二、【活动名称】：</span><span style="font-size: 20px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">2017年10月15日【红叶节】走红井路+游房山十渡，看遍山红叶</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">三、【活动地点】：门头沟--房山</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">四、【适合人群】：团队秋游，所有老少皆宜，走不都后面有车</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">五、【路程全长】：20公里，防火道，上升下降都不明显。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">六、【集合地点】：惠新西街南口出C口·<span style="line-height: 30px">公主坟新兴宾馆</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">七、【活动领队】：张姐 &nbsp;13381033689 ，13001927001&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">八、【咨询电话】： 010-84896319/20/21</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">参加活动的朋友请加</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;QQ</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">群 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;徒步网一群：94419616</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">微博 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@中国徒步网</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">微信 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;微信号：chinawalking</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif">二维码</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 18px"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><span style="font-size: 24px">&nbsp;http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/forum_travelview.php?newsid=61</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 20px">张姐户外简历</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 20px"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 20px">【红井路】房山区红井路是一条蜿蜒盘旋于北京房山区崇山峻岭中的一条乡村公路。它起于十渡镇卧龙村红港口，止于108国道霞云岭乡井儿峪，道路全长18.94公里，是连接房山区西北部G108国道与西南部涞宝路的重要通道。<br/>经北京市发改委批准，房山区红井路由房山区十渡镇政府负责建设实施，于2009年5月20日开工，2010年10月15日完工。<br/>起始于十渡镇卧龙村红港口终于108国道霞云岭乡井儿峪，道路全长18.94公里，是连接房山区西北部G108国道与西南部涞宝路的重要通道，交通意义重大。<br/>红井路最高点在14公里处，海拔905米，目前，在此赴京修建了观景台，一条依山而行的观景步道正在修建。站在稍显简陋的观景台上，环顾四周，大有“一览众山小”的感觉。<br/>近几年，很多旅游爱好者，特别是自驾游和骑行者都选择这条公路。红井路沿途，是至今为止保持最完整的原生态区域，除了新建的公路以外，没有任何被人为开发的痕迹，是一处很好的旅游胜地。特别是10-11月，满山的红叶更是让人流连忘返。此线路适合新人和团体秋游，走不动后面有车跟着。<br/></span></p><p><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170823/20170823211356_20535.jpg" alt="" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170823/20170823211356_16861.jpg" alt="" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170823/20170823211357_13501.jpg" alt="" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;line-height: 30px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-size: 20px">【房山十渡】十渡风景区位于北京市房山区西南，是中国北方唯一一处大规模喀斯特岩溶地貌。十渡风景区是中国国家AAAA景区和中国国家地质公园。2006年9月17日，联合国教科文组织正式批准中国房山世界地质公园并授牌。<br/>公园的申报成功，为北京增加了一处以自然景观为主的科技型世界地质公园，也使北京由此成为世界上第一个拥有“世界地质公园”的首都城市。房山世界地质公园共有八个园区，其中十渡为八个园区的核心园区——十渡园区。京津冀年票有效，没有年票的自由选择。<br/><img src="http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/UploadFile/image/20170823/20170823211448_20847.jpg" alt="" style=";padding: 0px;border-width: initial;border-style: none"/></span></p><p><br/></p>', '8', 1, '2017-10-15', '2017-10-15', 80, '北京,东城区', '红井路，十渡（京津冀年票', '休闲,穿越,徒步,摄影,聚会,体育健身', '2017-10-15 08:30:12', '惠新西街南口出C口，公主坟新兴宾馆', '1', '20KM', '汽车', 50, 0, '18328402805', '小树苗领队', '1504877324.jpg#1504877328.jpg#1504877333.jpg#1504877340.jpg', '观红叶，交友，聚会，徒步，京津冀年票有效，团队秋游', '2017-09-08 13:29:22'),
