3, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">9:30</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">到达红叶区。（一部分人走景区买票进入，一部分人从后山登山，有点小难度，一定带拐杖和穿登山鞋）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 8px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 20px;">12</span><strong><span style="font-size: 20px;">:00 &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">中饭自备。（景区里有特色农家饭，不贵自理）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 8px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">14:00&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">下午继续登景区的山）。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 8px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">16:00&nbsp;</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">上车返京（早的话去韩村河，有京津冀年票带上）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; text-indent: 8px; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">18:00</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;">到北京</span></strong></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-2" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">费用说明</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">费用总计：会员80元 &nbsp;（20人以下90）</span></strong><span style="font-size: 21px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">包括：车费、保险、2瓶水、资料。早的话去韩村河，有京津冀年票带上</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">不含门票：大概20元，请带上各种优待证，70岁以上免，学生半价，进景区被查按实际门票价格付。</span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-3" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">线路描述</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">一、【活动时间】： &nbsp;2017年 &nbsp;10月 22 日</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">二、【活动名称】：</span><span style="font-size: 20px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">房山坡峰岭赏红叶休闲一日活动</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">三、【活动地点】：房山区棺材山附近</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">四、【适合人群】：适合带新人，新人走景区买门票，老会员不走景区，最后穿进景区。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">五、【路程全长】：15公里，上升500--600米。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">六、【集合地点】：惠新西街南口出C口、公主坟新兴宾馆</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">七、【活动领队】：张姐 &nbsp;13381033689 &nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">八、【咨询电话】： 010-84896319/20</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">参加活动的朋友请加</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; QQ</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">群 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;徒步网一群：94419642</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">微博 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@中国徒步网</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">微信 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;微信号：chinawalking</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">二维码</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); line-height: 30px; font-size: 24px;">http://www.chinawalking.net.cn/forum_travel</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); line-height: 1.5; font-size: 24px;">view.php?newsid=61张姐户外简历</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Tahoma, Verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">赤橙黄绿青蓝紫，谁持彩练当空舞?与香山的红叶相比，坡峰岭的红叶却别有一番情致。如果说深秋香山是“万山红遍，层林浸染”，那么坡峰岭则是“红叶绿中游，彩练当空舞”，红、黄、绿、粉、黑，与蓝天、白云交相辉映，远远望去，犹如条条彩练当空飞舞，成为流动的色彩海洋。艳丽的色彩源自这里种类丰富的植物资源。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">坡起处多以柿树、核桃、桃树、山杏、杨树分布，伴生野酸枣、野山梨、野山菊等。半坡抬阶而上，蜿蜒小路两侧以自然生高大黄栌为重多，伴生麻榆、麻全子、酸枣、山荆等。高坡处又以高大黄栌、栾树、杨树密集分布，密而不见天日，为小憩休闲放松之圣地。其中，红叶有元宝枫、黄栌、火炬等七八个品种、数万株。纵览景区，是春季踏青观花、夏季避暑乘凉、秋季赏漫山红叶、冬季观瑞雪奇景的佳选。</span></p></div></div></div><p><br/></p>', '8', 1, '2017-10-22', '2017-10-22', 230, '北京,房山区', '房山--坡峰岭', '徒步,登山,穿越', '2017-10-22 09:00:00', '惠新西街南口，公主坟新兴宾馆', '1.0', '15km', '汽车', 34, 0, '18328402805', '苗子领队', '1504877606.jpg', '训练登山技巧', '2017-09-08 13:33:30');
INSERT INTO `tubuhuodong` (`id`, `title`, `tuwen`, `types`, `howlong`, `startday`, `endday`, `price`, `mudidi`, `jingdian`, `neirong`, `jihetime`, `jihedidian`, `qiangdu`, `juli`, `jiaotong`, `need`, `baoming`, `phone`, `leader`, `pictures`, `tese`, `ptime`) VALUES
(18, '2017年10月28-11月2日四川四姑娘山+峨眉山活动', '<h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">行程安排</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 9px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px">【活动路线】：四川成都</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">—峨眉山---日隆县---四姑娘山4300营地—登顶5025下到日隆— 时间允许走一个沟—--成都解散</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 16px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-size: 24px">【详细行程】</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D1/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 24px">（10月28日） ——</span><span style="font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 24px">成都集合后直奔乐山县 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -------宿峨眉山下或山上</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">先适应一下高反，看时间，争取宿到山上，</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">峨眉山金顶海拔3077米，适应高反，山上住宿很多，能走多高住多高，早休息</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D2/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 24px">（10月29日）</span><span style="font-size: 24px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 24px">——登顶后下山 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------宿峨眉山下</span></span></strong></p><p><span style="font-size: 24px;line-height: 36px;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)">山下有温泉，休整一下返成都（5人以上送温泉）</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D3/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">（10月30日）——成都--卧龙--日隆镇　 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------宿日隆镇（海拔3000米）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 39px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">适应高反，看队员情况和时间再定，学习装备使用，抓紧时间有可能上到4300营地。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 40px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D4/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">（10月31日）——四姑娘山大峰 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ----- 登顶下撤（5025-3000）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 24px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">看队员情况，不行的骑马，登顶是一对一高山向导陪同，确保大家安全，身体不行马上下撤大本营4300米。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 24px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D5/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">（11月1日）—— 看时间，走一个沟（共有3个沟） &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-------</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">宿日隆县（3000米）</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px"><span style="font-family: arial, 宋体, sans-serif;line-height: 24px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong>双桥沟、长坪沟选一个沟溜溜。</strong></span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">D6/</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">（11月2日）——日隆----成都 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 24px">轻松游玩，欢送会，畅谈总结，买下午或晚上的火车或飞机。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 32px;background: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><br/></p><h3 style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;height: 45px;line-height: 45px;color: rgb(75, 142, 232);font-weight: normal;font-size: 18px">费用说明</h3><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Tahoma, Verdana;text-indent: 2em;background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &#39;microsoft yahei&#39;;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);font-size: 24px">费用：6800元/人；</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0