t-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">/（12</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">月3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">日）上午去黄石寨，下午去天门山。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">　</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ------宿景区外三星标准</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">D</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">/（12</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">月4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">日）早起杨家寨、袁家寨、天子山、武陵源景区出直接去凤凰古城</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ---</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">--&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">宿凤凰古城</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">D5/(12月5日)上午参观凤凰古城，下午出发去德夯苗寨走一个峡谷 &nbsp;</span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-----宿苗寨体验民俗风情</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">D6/（12月6日）继续在苗寨，走另一个峡谷瀑布穿越到几斗苗寨，定该天吉首的K474火车票，送到车站</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;-----宿火车上</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p16" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 35px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;">D7/(12月7日) 中午回到北京</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-weight: bold; font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-2" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">费用说明</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 7px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">【活动费用】：</span><span class="15" style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;2380</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">元/人；</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></strong></p><p class="p17" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 24px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">费用包括：包含</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">四晚住宿2晚三星，</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">正餐</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">8顿，早餐4顿（爬山中午餐要自备，火车上不含）</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">、</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">当地</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">包车、</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">水、门票（含张家界，天门山，德夯苗寨大门票）</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">保险等。</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></strong></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">其他自理</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">费用</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">：</span><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">景点要想细看要自己付费，不含门票里。去张家界来回交通费自理，往返火车大概800元。</span></strong></p><div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><strong><br/></strong></div></div></div></div><div class="mdd-item" id="d-hd-3" style="margin: 0px 0px 35px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: auto; overflow: hidden; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, Arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;"><div class="title" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 672px; height: 45px; border-bottom: 1px dashed rgb(75, 142, 232);"><h3 style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; height: 45px; line-height: 45px; color: rgb(75, 142, 232); font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px;">线路描述</h3></div><div class="mdd-item-con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; line-height: 30px;"><div class="con" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 24px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 16px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 黑体;"><strong><span style="font-size: 18px;">连续6年经典线路</span></strong>-----张家界许多人都去过，但行走的路线不一样，中国徒步网将带你走不一样的路线，游遍张家界，不走常规路，不坐缆车，需要你有一定的体能，并且经常户外。（红色达级线路）</span></p><p class="p15" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 24px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 16px; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">一、【活动时间】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;&nbsp;2017</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">年 12</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">月</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;1--7</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">日</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;（坐飞机的2号上午12点到张家界集合）</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 二、【活动</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">名称</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">张家界户外游，天门山+</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">芙蓉镇+</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">德夯苗寨</span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 三、【活动</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">地点</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">湖南张家界，湘西凤凰古城，吉首德夯苗寨</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 四、【</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">适合</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">人群】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">运动型、经常户外 &nbsp;CVA：1.5级</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 五、【</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">路程全长</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">连续四天徒步每天15-20公里，张家界和德夯苗寨上升700--1000米 。</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 六、【集合地点】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">北京---张家界---吉首火车返京</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 七、【活动领队】：</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">张姐 &nbsp;13381033689</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 八、【咨询电话】： 010-84896319/20</span><span style="font-size: 19px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;">参加活动的朋友请加</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;">QQ<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">群 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 徒步网主群：94419616</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-indent: 2em; font-family: tahoma, verdana; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><span style="font-size: 24px; color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;">&nbsp; &nbsp;微博 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;@<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">中国徒步网</span></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 62, 140); font-family: tahoma;"></span></p><p class="p0" style="ma