="margin: 8px 0px 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px; padding-left: 0px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>大七孔景区</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">▲谁都没想到，此时此刻，竟然下起了大雨。我们躲进了一个凹进去的山体中间，等雨停。无聊之际，我让杰哥帮我拍照，这张成品的背后，就是无数张废片呐哈哈哈哈<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/6@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_229263570" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin: 0px 0px 18px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; background-color: transparent; outline: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/B7/FE/wKgBZ1l8D8aAMxW4ABbs52-d8no14.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/>