8px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/58/wKgBZ1mOTU6AN9nBAA30IoQ9sXo57.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">此时莲花是一片盛开，遮天蔽日的莲叶中缀着朵朵清莲，<br/>层层花瓣舒展着，纯洁又绚烂。</p><div id="_j_photo_233912846" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/6B/wKgBZ1mOTV6ADoDIAAdFa_Hnwdc36.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_233912847" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/7E/wKgBZ1mOTXCAd-1RAAoqek565GU39.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_233912848" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/9B/wKgBZ1mOTY2ASUA1AA6q_2c4GLQ17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">因为姓连，所以看到采莲桥就一定要跑去拍一张~<br/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">翠湖公园并不很大，转过一圈后便出发去<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">云南</a>大学。<br/>跟着导航从翠湖公园到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">云南</a>大学没用几分钟便到了~<br/><br/></p><div id="_j_paragraph_4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F3/96/wKgBZ1msCGSAMrc4AAFVKs_qDRI51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="· 云南大学" alt="· 云南大学"/></div><div id="_j_photo_233912849" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/C2/wKgBZ1mOTaWAYCXlAA2Hf_TL4_A46.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">云南</a>大学的大门在一片苍翠的绿荫之中，她的庄严与沧桑，不是任何用华丽砖墙所垒砌的建筑所能比拟的。<br/>就像一位老者，只在那里一站，傲然风骨尽显眼前。</p><div id="_j_photo_233912852" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D7/2A/wKgBZ1mOTeqAUJrQAAzfhqKc7qY59.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">红白相间的配色是格外让人喜欢的，时光为年代久远的砖墙布上斑斑驳驳的印记。<br/>树影洒下，时而有穿着学士服的学生在这里拍照留念，能在这样的学校度过四年学生时光，想想也是件幸福的事~<br/><br/>之前去了<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">厦门</a>大学之后跟妈妈说，就应该在高中的时候带着孩子去各个大学转转，好受激励一定要在美美的地方上大学~<br/>我如今是没机会啦，但是能在一个阳光正好的午后漫步于此，也觉幸运。</p><div id="_j_photo_233912851" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D7/0B/wKgBZ1mOTdOAE-sqAApnVY0AQoI17.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 1020px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">一只装酷的连连~</p><div id="_j_photo_233912853" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D7/36/wKgBZ1mOTfmAOlY_AAmvv18k0gI23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_233912854" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D7/48/wKgBZ1mOTguADc5CAArOy3nO0rg30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_233912855" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">田田的叶子总是让人喜欢。<br/>绿叶的发青，繁茂，勃<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">勃生</a>机，总能让我雀跃起来~</p><div id="_j_photo_233912850" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D6/EC/wKgBZ1mOTb2AebW0AArCK5dV46U73.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_233912856" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="http://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/D7/9A/wKgBZ1mOTjKAckLPAApsvMmh5ic33.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">和黑黑在云大里走走停停，拍拍照，像极了上大学时和艳儿在学校里散步的悠闲午后，<br/>那样的日子总是好的不真实，大概学校就是那么一个让人做梦的地方，<br/>此时此景，梦一场又何妨呢。</p><div id="_j_photo_233912857" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南大学</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">离开云大，决定去金马碧鸡坊吃些东西，一眼看到桥香园过桥米线，便一定要尝尝的了。<br/></p><div id="_j_paragraph_5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/F9/D1/wKgBZ1msDaGAZtf2AAFsHVnicaI32.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="· 金马碧鸡坊" alt="· 金马碧鸡坊"/></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><br/>过桥米线分很多种，秀才、举人、进士、状元，配菜量与价格各不相同。<br/>我们两选择了进士的套餐，35元一份，除了米线以外还配有一份汽锅鸡。</p><div id="_j_photo_233912858" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;"></a></div><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:30:55', '云南十日 | 予你一片温柔的蓝之梦', '1504881052.jpeg', 0);
INSERT INTO `youji` (`id`, `uid`, `tuwen`, `type`, `ytime`, `title`, `pic`, `readcnt`) VALUES
(17, 7, '<p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大理</a>贰日匆匆一瞥，带来首次「蜂首」纪念。<br/>无法否认，哪怕生活或多或少不如意，但会相逢这样的人生小惊喜，<br/>就是活着折腾的最佳佐证，和意义。</p><div id="_j_photo_229248230" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AB/A3/wKgBZ1l7_t6AflJlAETQLtSQ1nA448.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>海东镇</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_229248240" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AC/5D/wKgBZ1l7_9-AKK-PAEl0rT7K7_Y737.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>海东镇</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_229471534" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 1