ag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>大理古城</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_229912228" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>大理古城</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_229686991" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>大理古城</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230474763" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>才村</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">二十年前，<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">云南</a>初印象源于娘亲的一次旅行，<br/>那时<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大理</a><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">丽江</a>尚未全面开发旅游，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">香格里拉</a>也还只称「中甸」，<br/>那时家里只有胶片机，还没办法无节制咔嚓咔嚓要倒数着数字留影，<br/>娘亲说，那可真是世外<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">桃源</a>。<br/><br/>二十年间，<br/>娘亲又陆续去了<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">云南</a>五次，<br/>最近一次从<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">丽江</a>回来谈起感受，只有淡淡的「认不得了」四个字。<br/><br/>原来，<br/>旅行中曾给你以震撼感动的地方，最难得的是重逢时还能道一句，别来无恙。<br/><br/></p><div id="_j_paragraph_2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><img src="https://p4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/89/30/wKgBZ1l-1uuAf1X4AACJdhrR2WE442.png?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fh%2F150%2Fq%2F90" class="no_word _j_anchor" title="叭哒 | 告别智能生活两天" alt="叭哒 | 告别智能生活两天"/></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">【这一点都不热的轻轻的夏天啊】<br/>估计脑洞再大，也从没想过会来<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大理</a>度个周末，<br/>一次公差过后，<br/>紧接一个双休日，<br/>脚已踩在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">昆明</a>，<br/>面对那么不热的，轻轻的夏天，<br/>实在不舍得直接回到气温已飙升40度的魔都当宅女。</p><div id="_j_photo_230108363" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>云南陆军讲武堂旧址</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230108366" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" alt="" style="height: 472px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>翠湖公园</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">【拜拜了万能的手机】<br/>车票，客栈，三下五除二顺利搞定，<br/>一个人出门就此最为省心。<br/><br/>准备检票上车之际，<br/>「上厕所」这件小事转变了之后两天的基调，<br/>提裤子，啪哒，咕咚，<br/>棒呆，<br/>手机滑入茅坑这种一向只活在朋友圈里的事情，<br/>带着一个奸笑来到我身边。<br/><br/>过程不可说不可说，</p><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:32:31', '大理轻夏，苍洱二日谈', '1504881149.png', 22);
INSERT INTO `youji` (`id`, `uid`, `tuwen`, `type`, `ytime`, `title`, `pic`, `readcnt`) VALUES
(18, 7, '<div id="_j_paragraph_2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t9" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 50px; display: block;">开篇碎碎念</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;一直有一个想法，就是结婚后不去影楼拍婚纱照，而是两个人带上单反和三脚架去蜜月旅拍婚纱照。今年3月8日结婚后，这个想法就提上议程了，选来选去，最后决定了去<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">普吉岛</a>。5月的时候，当时在准备考雅思，但一直分心在准备机票和酒店，不过幸好没有影响到雅思的发挥。因为不知道什么时候放暑假，老公也只能请3天的婚假，所以我们的蜜月之旅加加埋埋只有4天的时间。不过能安排好行程辛苦一点，4天也能玩出一个月的感觉，哈哈<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/1@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/>！<br/></p><div id="_j_paragraph_3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t9" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 50px; display: block;">准备</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">机票：亚航，8月29日<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">香港</a>——布吉，9月2日布吉——<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">香港</a>。<br/>酒店：深绿度假村（The&nbsp;Viridian&nbsp;Resort）四晚含早729rmb，蚂蜂窝订的。<br/>签证：刚好在免签证费期间，而且抢到了邮政的一元签证，所以就一元签好了。<br/>行李：我没买托运，两个人带了两个20寸的箱子，一人背一个背包直接登机。<br/>钱：在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">中国</a>银行换了10000泰铢，2070人民币，其实不担心，因为普吉到处都能用微信和支付宝支付，超方便！！！<br/>接送：佰程订的接机（89rmb）和送机（99rmb）<br/>出海：大小皇帝岛，懒猫订的泰浪号+1次深潜，599rmb一人，加拍照1500泰铢，拍完后直接给教练的<br/>按摩：佰程订的东方spa泰式按摩两小时（因为我们迟到了，所以只能按一个小时<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/21@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/>，哭！）106rmb一人<br/>射击：咔咔旅游订的我们买了一个.38，一个.45和一个轻火力，.38和.45是重火力149人民币10发子弹，轻火力那个98rmb10发。<br/>租摩托车：就在酒店外面一些订门票的地方租的，压的护照，300泰铢24小时。<br/>电话卡：淘宝买的happy卡<br/>地图APP：探途离线地图，超好用，不用联网，我一直是靠它导航的。</p><div id="_j_paragraph_4" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t9" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 50px; display: block;">行程安排</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">Day1:芭<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">东海</a>滩——拉<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">威海</a>鲜市场<br/>Day2：大小皇帝岛——东方spa马杀鸡<br/>Day3：甲途射击中心——普吉镇——王权免税店<br/>Day4：卡隆海滩<br/></p><div id="_j_paragraph_5" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t9" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 24px; height: 50px; background: 0px center; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); line-height: 50px;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 50px; display: block;">❀Day0（8月29日）</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><br/>7点30分到达机场，领完登机牌后就在7-11吃了一个鸡腿，后来就一直对这个鸡腿念念不忘了，后来回到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">香港</a>又吃了一个<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/1@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><br/></p><div id="_j_photo_242079479" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AB/23/wKgBZ1mtT6KAXEHbAAIzH5wGLK480.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153,