style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -25px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>深绿度假村</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">吃完早餐就回房间梳妆打扮啦！因为老公有长发情结，而且我也觉得长发拍婚纱比较好看就带了假发，缺点是超！级！热！<br/></p><div id="_j_photo_242083869" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AD/8B/wKgBZ1mtUniABpyuAAVZjOy8GZ411.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="hotel" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -25px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>深绿度假村</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_242083870" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AD/8E/wKgBZ1mtUn2AXxsqAARYcL3SlSE81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="hotel" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -25px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>深绿度假村</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_242083871" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AD/91/wKgBZ1mtUoGAYX1oAAau08g2Mi454.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 906px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="hotel" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -25px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>深绿度假村</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_242083872" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/AD/95/wKgBZ1mtUoWAcxUJAAcl1U9ZRpk06.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 510px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="hotel" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -25px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>深绿度假村</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">在阳台自拍，用八爪鱼把相机固定在栏杆上<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/79@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_242083873" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;"></a></div><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:33:51', '泰国普吉岛四天四夜蜜月之旅——自拍旅拍婚纱照', '1504881229.jpeg', 0);
INSERT INTO `youji` (`id`, `uid`, `tuwen`, `type`, `ytime`, `title`, `pic`, `readcnt`) VALUES
(19, 7, '<p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">新疆</a>，几乎蕴藏着<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">中国</a>夏天最美好的那些部分。以前离<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">新疆</a>最近的地方，是我家楼下的那个烤羊肉串摊，没想过有天会真正地连续吃半个月羊肉。</p><div id="_j_photo_230903645" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 640px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/04/15/wKgBZ1mClsKAFD3zAADDTgL0IAM34.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 640px; width: 640px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>成都火车北站</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">而这一切的开始，要从我坐上K2060次列车说起……<br/><br/>尽管我知道飞机是最快捷的方式，但一个恐飞的我，还是选择47小时的火车，我对自己的安慰说法是：“可以看尽一路的人文风情与地貌变化”。</p><div id="_j_photo_230904153" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 640px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/04/54/wKgBZ1mClwOAExc0AAD3o8uuJFs93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 380px; width: 640px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>西宁火车站</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">尽管我知道飞机是最快捷的方式，但一个恐飞的我，还是选择47小时的火车，我对自己的安慰说法是：“可以看尽一路的人文风情与地貌变化”。<br/><br/>一路我看到了丘陵变成戈壁，戈壁变成雪山，雪山变成沙漠，沙漠变成草原，然后广播提醒我<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">乌鲁木齐</a>到了。</p><div id="_j_paragraph_1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t6" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t6.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 120px; margin-left: 70px;">第一天 天山／天池</span></h2></div><div class="add_video _j_seqitem " style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; width: 680px; height: 400px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><video src="http://www.mafengwo.cn/rest/app/note/video/1E1E6E6CED470F969C33DC5901307461?jsondata=%7B%22data_style%22%3A%22direct%22%7D" width="680" height="420" controls="controls" class="_j_videoplayer"></video></div><div id="_j_photo_230905275" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/40/F9/wKgBZ1loy5KAck55ABCsFhdIcQY23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>天山天池风景区</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">天池，论海拔的话，还真的是在天上。和大多数的空中湖泊一样，天池也就看看山和水，而让人喜出望外的是，旁边的树林，有别样的美。</p><div id="_j_photo_230905844" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/6C/wKgBZ1mCmDeAdlCjAA8He-WkITY07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>天山天池风景区</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230905845" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/71/wKgBZ1mCmDyAFlgUAA7QVKE3el085.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>天山天池风景区</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230905846" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/73/wKgBZ1mCmD-AMn0PAA3iqrL6FGs58.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>天山天池风景区</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230905848" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/05/82/wKgBZ1mCmE-AKaxSAAzxBR7giKY19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>天山天池风景区</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">不是选择景区人流最多的地方，而是在旁边的一片小树林，阳光洒下来，不一样的美。</p><div id="_j_paragraph_2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t6" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t6.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 120px; margin-left: 70px;">第二天 塔城地区</span></h2></div><div id="_j_photo_230906656" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/06/06/wKgBZ1mCmPmAWkz6AA1kCsXbrv438.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" target="_blank" class="_j_anchor" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>克拉玛依</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">第二天因为要去到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">布尔津</a>，从<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">乌鲁木齐</a>过去，穿越<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">克拉玛依</a>，大概会花到8个小时的车程，所以整个一天基本都在车上，还好沿途的风景很漂亮，也不至于枯燥无味。</p><div id="_j_photo_230907663" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/06/5D/wKgBZ1mCmWaAffrbAA6Of8DIxMU64.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">在开了几百公里之后，我们发现了路边有这样一个地方，孤独的几座农家小屋。尽管当时的油不多了，<br/>但我们还忍不住停留了一会儿。</p><div id="_j_photo_230907661" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/06/51/wKgBZ1mCmVmAT-DrABBuoc_Ncr048.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><div id="_j_photo_230907664" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/06/61/wKgBZ1mCmW2ADGb_ABQzs387GDE41.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><div id="_j_photo_230907666" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/06/7A/wKgBZ1mCmYqAZ0S_AA3Wy4zaFYQ04.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><div id="_j_paragraph_3" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t6" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t6.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: center;"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 95px; display: block; margin-right: 120px; margin-left: 70px;">第三天 禾木/喀纳斯</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">由于<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">禾木</a>和<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">喀纳斯</a>是挨着很近的，所以第三天的安排相对是最紧凑的。</p><div id="_j_photo_230908755" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/18/wKgBZ1mCmkaAKJu1ABZWPbCjKTE83.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">禾木</a>公路，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">新疆</a>最美三大公路之一，沿途的风景可以说是看不够，遗憾的是没有带航拍，不然出片又是另一种感觉。</p><div id="_j_photo_230909480" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://p3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/83/40/wKgBZ1lkKPGAfXCsAA9mH00wqS435.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">翻过山后，便是草原。</p><div id="_j_photo_230909869" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/B0/wKgBZ1mCmxCANKsqAA5aOlyCajY69.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><div id="_j_photo_230909870" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/07/C8/wKgBZ1mCmy6AUZO-ABDERRk4OOg20.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-he