rsor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="house" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) 0px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>禾木村</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_230915773" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/72/9C/wKgBZ1lc7zKACO0_ABLGqVL5lGI92.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 382px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">观赏<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">禾木</a>村的最佳地点是远处的一座山上，所以你得花半个小时爬上去。<br/>在天空下起小雨的时候，我们下了山，驱车前往<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">喀纳斯</a>。</p><div id="_j_photo_230915775" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;"></a></div><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:34:52', '我行走在了新疆最美的天地间，北疆游记', '1504881290.jpeg', 5);
INSERT INTO `youji` (`id`, `uid`, `tuwen`, `type`, `ytime`, `title`, `pic`, `readcnt`) VALUES
(20, 7, '<p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">相机：Canon&nbsp;5D&nbsp;Mark&nbsp;Ⅲ&nbsp;+&nbsp;Canon&nbsp;EOS&nbsp;5<br/>镜头：Canon&nbsp;35mm&nbsp;&nbsp;f1.4&nbsp;Ⅱ＋70-200mm&nbsp;f2.8&nbsp;&nbsp;IS&nbsp;Ⅱ＋16-35mm&nbsp;f4&nbsp;+50mm&nbsp;f1.8&nbsp;stm</p><div id="_j_photo_227699874" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/51/A5/wKgBZ1l1Yy2AKcGXABdBFONl9CY30.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 524px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">出行准备（交通，住宿）</p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/114@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/>选择飞机出行的小伙伴可以试试先飞到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>再动车到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>，查了几家旅行网站，飞机到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>的价格比飞机到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>的价格低了几百。<br/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/240@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>的景点基本都分布在市区，而且市区也不大，所以住宿一般会放在春熙路，宽窄巷子和锦里附近，我选择的是春熙路附近。</p><div id="_j_paragraph_1" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t8" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t8.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 110px; display: block; margin-right: 70px; margin-left: 35px;">DAY 1 重庆——成都</span></h2></div><div id="_j_photo_227706351" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/92/wKgBZ1l1aKGATDw0AAk0aw6RapE87.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 376px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>重庆火车北站</a></span></div><div id="_j_photo_227706352" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/9C/wKgBZ1l1aKqAS4BgAAlwsVtdAZY23.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>重庆火车北站</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">经历了一天一夜的火车终于到了<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>，准备去吃一顿去年在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>没来得及吃的九宫格火锅，选择的是<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>火锅扛把子——佩姐老火锅。</p><div id="_j_photo_227706353" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/B5/wKgBZ1l1aMqAHFk0ABNDK8oa_Qk53.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 426px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>重庆火车北站</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>的打的费用真的比<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">杭州</a>低很多<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/5@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227706354" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/56/BC/wKgBZ1l1aNKAbTZpAAnflpP-hg867.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">打的十几分钟就到了佩姐老火锅，九宫格走起<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/25@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227708191" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/58/21/wKgBZ1l1aiOAKJ6pAAp4t_UzuTI51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">食材很新鲜，点的微辣锅底，两个人吃得快被辣哭了，对不怎么会吃辣的小伙伴不太友好。中规中矩没有想象中特别好的味道，上次来<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>吃的晓宇火锅也比佩姐好吃得多，摊手<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/131@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227708192" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/58/38/wKgBZ1l1ajaAEGTGABApvB-lr2s19.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><div id="_j_photo_227708193" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/58/48/wKgBZ1l1akSAA3bHAA17PPIHNp893.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 430px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">吃完火锅就出发去<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>了，想看<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>深度游的小伙伴，麻烦移步我的<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>攻略<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/5@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">坐动车2小时就能到达<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>，还是挺方便的。</p><div id="_j_photo_227710206" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5A/39/wKgBZ1l1bFyAHXbqAA1Fo8nurG038.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 453px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="traffic" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -100px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>成都火车北站</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">放下行李，休息了下就去觅食了<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/20@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">韩包子，老牌<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>包子店，果断点了以店名命名的韩包子，皮薄肉多，汤汁四溢，口感绝佳，推荐。这家店也有卖担担面，甜水面之类的小吃，由于要留肚子给别的美食就没点了，小伙伴可以自己去探店。<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227712138" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5B/73/wKgBZ1l1beeAS8hPABS8KUB_EZQ82.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>韩包子(春熙路店)</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>和<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>都随处可见的一只酸奶牛，点了招牌紫米酸奶，紫米料足，有嚼劲，酸奶不是特别甜，价格也不贵，随处可见的消暑饮品，推荐<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/20@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/><br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227712139" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: po