x; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://a2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5B/A3/wKgBZ1l1bimAbIhBAAuQ-PUyfyI99.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 993px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="shopping" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -125px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>春熙路</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">春熙路夜景</p><div id="_j_photo_227712144" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5B/BB/wKgBZ1l1bjqALvA3ABMUVBdU-U487.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 432px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="shopping" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -125px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>春熙路</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">点了赖汤圆的特色赖汤圆，名气大于味道，一股速冻汤圆的味道，差评，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">宁波</a>汤圆甩这个汤圆几条街。<br/>地址：&nbsp;总府路23号(春熙路太平洋百货对面)<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/brands_v2/14@2x.png" style="width: 28px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227712145" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5B/C5/wKgBZ1l1bkGALK-WAAp5B4PLXqY05.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>赖汤圆(总府路店)</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>老字号煎蛋面，网上很多人推荐，个人觉得太油腻，这种面还是清淡点比较好，不过味道还可以。<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_227712146" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/5B/CB/wKgBZ1l1bkuARLVvABAhUyaL7AI93.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>华兴街煎蛋面(总店)</a></span></div><div id="_j_paragraph_2" class="article_title _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal;"><h2 class="t8" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 22px; height: 86px; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/t8.gif&quot;) 0px 0px no-repeat; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);"><span class="_j_anchor" style="line-height: 110px; display: block; margin-right: 70px; margin-left: 35px;">DAY 2 人民公园 宽窄巷子 武侯祠 锦里</span></h2></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">今天主要是为了感受<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>的慢生活，所以早上决定去人民公园喝喝茶<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/79@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>老字号糕点铺，很多分店，味道好，料足，价格亲民，喜欢糕点的小伙伴不要错过，回去的时候买点当伴手礼相当不错。图上的是蛋黄酥。<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_228002967" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/31/D3/wKgBZ1l2tBiAUdNWAA_Vn7YHLHQ51.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>宫廷糕点</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>街景，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>的共享单车普及率特别高，而且用单车出行特别方便，我在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>基本都是滴滴和ofo。</p><div id="_j_photo_228002968" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://p2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/31/D6/wKgBZ1l2tBqAQ6hlAAoi10RKtZM86.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 401px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">小民堂的手工甜水面，好吃得不要不要的，甜甜咸咸辣辣，对第一次吃到甜水面的我来说很难形容味道，真的很好吃，强烈推荐，第一个满分推荐就是它了。<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/30@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/30@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/30@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/30@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/30@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><div id="_j_photo_228005457" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/33/75/wKgBZ1l2tZ2Ac2scAAoZ19eP8JU03.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 467px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>小名堂担担甜水面(东城根上街店)</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">小民堂的凉糕，糯，有嚼劲，红糖味道超级浓，对于我这种喜甜的人说简直不要太好吃，推荐。<br/>推荐指数：<img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/><img src="http://images.mafengwo.net/images/i/face/daily_v2/43@2x.png" style="width: 23px;"/></p><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">这家分店是东城根上街店，离人民公园只有几十米的距离。</p><div id="_j_photo_228004415" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/32/FD/wKgBZ1l2tRuAbFMeAAoxQ4Pgpt033.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F680%2Fq%2F90" alt="" style="height: 680px; width: 680px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a><span class="pic_tag" style="margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 24px; display: block; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px; width: 600px;"><a href="http://undefined" class="_j_anchor" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(153, 153, 153); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: inline-block; position: relative;"><em class="food" style="width: 24px; height: 24px; margin-right: 10px; display: inline-block; background: url(&quot;/images/post/new_notes/nn_v2/nn_sprite_v25.png&quot;) -50px -203px no-repeat; vertical-align: -6px;"></em>小名堂担担甜水面(东城根上街店)</a></span></div><p class="_j_note_content _j_seqitem" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;">吃完小名堂就去人民公园了，本地气息很浓的地方，能看到跳广场舞的，游船的，散步的，能感受到<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">成都</a>的“慢生活”。不需要门票。</p><div id="_j_photo_228120330" class="add_pic _j_anchorcnt _j_seqitem" style="margin-bottom: 18px; word-wrap: break-word; position: relative; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 15px; white-space: normal; width: 680px;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 138, 0); cursor: pointer; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; display: block; position: relative; zoom: 1;"></a></div><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:36:39', '蓉城印象，成都五天四晚深度游（详细行程定制与美食推荐', '1504881398.jpeg', 1);
INSERT INTO `youji` (`id`, `uid`, `tuwen`, `type`, `ytime`, `title`, `pic`, `readcnt`) VALUES
(21, 7, '<div class="post_info" style="padding-left: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; float: left; width: 600px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><div class="a_con_text cont" id="pnl_contentinfo" style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(77, 77, 77); line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px;"><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>有着绝美的夜景、火辣的火锅、漂亮的美女，活脱脱一个火辣辣的城市。不仅有山、水、林、泉、瀑、峡、洞等为一体的自然风光,也拥有丰富的历史文化景观,<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>的语言于饮食文化也是极大的特色。<br/>在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>的时候住的一家在洪崖洞旁边的青旅&nbsp;&nbsp;37度2艺术青年旅舍&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;老板是地道的<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>人，完全是个<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>通，给我们讲了好多<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>的玩的吃的。我们基本上就按老板说的在体验。<br/><br/>D1<br/>解放碑——<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">三峡</a>博物馆——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——洪崖洞<br/>D2<br/>涂鸦街——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——鹅岭公园<br/>D3<br/>洋人街——下浩<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">老街</a>——精典书店——南山——南滨路——长江索道<br/>D4<br/>解放碑——<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大学城</a>（美院）——磁器口——皇冠大扶梯——山<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">城步</a>道<br/><br/>如果还有什么想去的地方，就去<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>周边游走一下<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">武隆</a>仙女山&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">黑山</a>谷奥陶纪&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;北碚<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">偏岩古镇</a><br/>更多美丽的地方等你去发现<br/><br/><br/>D1<br/>解放碑——<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">三峡</a>博物馆——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——洪崖洞<br/><br/>解放碑：八一好吃街、人民公园掏耳朵、国泰大剧院(<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>美术馆)如果有展览可以去转转<br/>&nbsp;<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n4-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/BD/wKgBZ1ms2AGAJu8AAAJha1SnNK024.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://p1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/4A/96/wKgBZ1ms2VGAPzPZAAQWUCyjowE76.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">三峡</a>博物馆：解放碑有多路公交可以直接到达，去<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>人民大礼堂和<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">三峡</a>博物馆&nbsp;在一块地方（博物馆周一闭馆，请注意时间出行）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://b2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/C3/wKgBZ1ms2BCAf_dIAAB0jkNPyqo07.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 300px; width: 534px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">洪雅</a>洞：适合晚上去19：30开灯，23:00关灯，（最好不要在洪崖洞吃&nbsp;主食，味道一般）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://c3-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/48/CA/wKgBZ1ms1heAT6xHAAsEKm48k8k81.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><br/>逛完洪崖洞，晚上还可以坐&nbsp;&nbsp;两江夜游轮船（船票68—200元多不等），换个角度看<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/><br/>D2<br/>涂鸦街——李子坝——鹅岭二厂——鹅岭公园<br/><br/>涂鸦街：&nbsp;川美老校区，黄桷坪校区交通茶馆和涂鸦街<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="https://n2-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/49/FA/wKgBZ1ms2FmAPLLwAAF99FHUaEM97.jpeg?imageView2%2F2%2Fw%2F600%2Fq%2F90" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/><br/>李子坝：2号线轻轨站点(穿楼而过的轻轨站)<br/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>鹅岭二厂：李子坝站往山上走，穿过往上的楼梯，15分钟左右，就可以到达鹅岭二厂场文创园（从你的全世界路过拍摄地）&nbsp;，还有一家网红咖啡馆——懒鱼时光咖啡馆(适合拍照）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">鹅岭公园：晚上，就在二厂旁边的鹅岭公园可以鸟瞰<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>夜景，公园里有个高塔（门票5元）登塔上顶，视野非常开阔(个人认为比一棵树性价比高）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><br/><br/><br/>D3<br/><br/>洋人街——下浩<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">老街</a>——精典书店——南山——南滨路——长江索道<br/><br/>洋人街：公交乘坐公交去洋人街(适合拍照也是个游乐园)有世界上最大的厕所<br/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 367px; width: 490px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>下浩<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">老街</a>:另一个即将消失的十八梯，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">老街</a>老巷，<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>最原始的生活味道<br/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 800px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">精典书店：<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>文化地标，从1998年成立以来一直引领着这个城市的阅读生活，是一个写书人与读书人交汇的聚集地<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 301px; width: 465px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>&nbsp;<br/>南山：山上在黄桷垭<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">老街</a>&nbsp;有&nbsp;&nbsp;三毛故居&nbsp;.老君洞&nbsp;（老君洞的天王殿顶层可以鸟瞰<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>山城全景，关键是免费，开放时间8:00——17:30)<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 450px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>南山一棵树：<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>最大的山顶观景平台，最适合拍夜景（尽量避免周末去，人太多）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 334px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>南滨路：<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>最美的滨江路，拥有大型音乐喷泉，一路风景秀丽，夜景超美<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 398px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/><br/>长江索道：乘坐的时候最好是从南岸（<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">龙门</a>浩站点）往解放碑方向，南岸区站点一般不用排队，解放碑新华路站点乘坐人员一般都很多。<br/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 400px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>D4<br/>解放碑——<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大学城</a>（美院）——磁器口——皇冠大扶梯——山<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">城步</a>道<br/><br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大学城</a>：<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">大学城</a>(川美的<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">马赛</a>克墙)罗中立美术馆。川美湖区沿湖廊道<br/><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 366px; width: 550px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>磁器口：去磁器口(乘坐地铁1号线到磁器口站下车，咖啡店&nbsp;麻花&nbsp;）&nbsp;&nbsp;，大冰的小屋&nbsp;（沙坪坝区磁器口横街金碧桥2号）<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 449px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/>皇冠大扶梯：地铁1号线或轻轨3号线两路口站出来就到了<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 280px; width: 500px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;">&nbsp;<br/><br/>山城第三步道：入口在中兴路法院旁边，上口在<a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">重庆</a>七星岗地铁站附近<br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><a target="_blank" href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(255, 157, 0); cursor: pointer;"><img class="_j_lazyload" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==" style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; height: 399px; width: 600px; background: rgb(252, 242, 220); display: block;"/></a></p><p class="_j_note_content" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;"><br/><br/>4-5天后，就可以去周边了，有一日团可以报<br/><br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">武隆</a>仙女山<br/><a href="http://undefined" class="link _j_keyword_mdd" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(77, 77, 77); cursor: pointer; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(148, 142, 142);">黑山</a>谷奥陶纪玻璃栈道<br/></p></div><div class="integral" style="margin-top: 15px; margin-left: 10px; padding: 10px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; width: 500px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); color: rgb(229, 110, 2); position: relative;"><div class="legend" style="padding: 5px 10px; word-wrap: break-word; position: absolute; left: 30px; top: -15px;">获得积分</div><a href="http://undefined" style="color: rgb(229, 110, 2); cursor: pointer;"><span style="cursor: pointer;">发表游记</span><span style="color:#e56e02"><span style="cursor: pointer;">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;">+30</strong><span style="color:#e56e02"><span style="cursor: pointer;">&nbsp; &nbsp;文章被回复&nbsp;</span></span><strong style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); cursor: pointer;">3</strong></a></div></div><div class="clear" style="word-wrap: break-word; clear: both; height: 0px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; white-space: normal;"></div><p><br/></p>', 1, '2017-09-08 14:38:30', '重庆，非去不可（重庆自由行路线攻略）', '1504881509.jpeg', 10);

